OL,3,CWoman who survived stroke at 24 says
OL,4,Csinging helped her speak again
OL,6,FA young woman from Greater Manchester
OL,7,Fhas said singing her favourite songs
OL,8,Fhelped her find her voice again after
OL,9,Fsuffering a devastating stroke at just
OL,10,F24 years old.
OL,12,FSummer Clarke, now 26, from Denton,
OL,13,Fwas given just a 10% chance of
OL,14,Fsurvival after she suffered a
OL,15,Fspontaneous brain haemorrhage in 2022.
OL,16,FHer family were told to prepare for
OL,17,Fthe worst as doctors placed her in an
OL,18,Finduced coma to relieve pressure on
OL,19,Fher brain.
