OL,3,CWoman who survived stroke at 24 says
OL,4,Csinging helped her speak again
OL,6,FBut in a remarkable turn of events,
OL,7,FSummer defied the odds`and says
OL,8,Fsinging played a crucial role in her
OL,9,Frecovery.
OL,11,F"I couldn't talk, walk or even
OL,12,Frecognise my own mum," she said. "But
OL,13,FI could sing. It was the strangest
OL,14,Fthing`music just came naturally to me."
OL,16,FSummer's mother, Linda, remembers how
OL,17,Fher daughter, a former British Airways
OL,18,Fcabin crew member, began miming and
OL,19,Fsinging songs`even before she could
OL,20,Fspeak or understand basic language
OL,21,Fagain.
