OL,3,CWoman who survived stroke at 24 says
OL,4,Csinging helped her speak again
OL,6,FThe charity says Summer's experience
OL,7,Fis not unique. A new survey of stroke
OL,8,Fsurvivors has found more than a third
OL,9,F(35%) say they could sing more easily
OL,10,Fthan speak in the early stages of
OL,11,Frecovery. One in four said singing or
OL,12,Fhumming came before talking, and over
OL,13,F60% said music helped improve their
OL,14,Fcommunication skills.
