OL,3,CWoman who survived stroke at 24 says
OL,4,Csinging helped her speak again
OL,6,FSummer hopes her story will inspire
OL,7,Fothers to support the campaign`and to
OL,8,Fbelieve that recovery is possible.
OL,10,F"I'm still healing, but singing gave
OL,11,Fme a voice again," she said. "It gave
OL,12,Fme hope."
